body:
This release revert a breaking change with the ordering of `afterEach` calls.

Please see the [release notes](https://github.com/jasmine/jasmine/blob/master/release_notes/2.4.1.md)
This release only changes the bower package, for full details see the [release notes](https://github.com/jasmine/jasmine/blob/master/release_notes/2.3.1.md).
